songs.title: Callin’*
songs.lyrics:
Lyrics From Snippet

[Chorus: Lil Peep]
Callin', shawty callin’, why you call girl?
She can't understand me, she a fan girl
Big bands, getting big bands, but it come with
A whole lot of bullshit (What?), Tracy keep a full clip (Krah)
Pull up on your bitch and I flex like I'm made to (like I’m made to)
Pull up on your block with the squad like I hate you (like I hate you)
Work non-stop 'cause the clock don't stop (nah)
GothBoi, I don't need a Glock, my hitta' will mop you

[Verse 2: Gab3 & Lil Peep]
I make [?]
Now she selling I don't wanna talk shit (i don't wanna talk too)
I can't believe I lost you
Ridin’ ridin’, she back on the cough syrup (cough syrup)
I was smoking kush in the bathroom
